#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="an4.63"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an4.63:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 4 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 4 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.63:0.2"
msgid "7. Pattakammavagga "
msgstr "7. Deeds of Substance "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "an4.63:0.3"
msgid "63. Brahmasutta "
msgstr "63. Living with Brahmā "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "an4.63:1.1"
msgid "“Sabrahmakāni, bhikkhave, tāni kulāni yesaṃ puttānaṃ mātāpitaro ajjhāgāre pūjitā honti. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, a family where the children honor their parents in their home is said to live with Brahmā. "

msgctxt "an4.63:1.2"
msgid "Sapubbācariyakāni, bhikkhave, tāni kulāni, yesaṃ puttānaṃ mātāpitaro ajjhāgāre pūjitā honti. "
msgstr "A family where the children honor their parents in their home is said to live with the first teachers. "

#. VAR: Sapubbadevatāni → sapubbadevāni (s1-3, km)
msgctxt "an4.63:1.3"
msgid "Sapubbadevatāni, bhikkhave, tāni kulāni yesaṃ puttānaṃ mātāpitaro ajjhāgāre pūjitā honti. "
msgstr "A family where the children honor their parents in their home is said to live with the old deities. "

msgctxt "an4.63:1.4"
msgid "Sāhuneyyakāni, bhikkhave, tāni kulāni yesaṃ puttānaṃ mātāpitaro ajjhāgāre pūjitā honti. "
msgstr "A family where the children honor their parents in their home is said to live with those worthy of offerings dedicated to the gods. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
#. VAR: mātāpitūnaṃ → mātāpitunnaṃ (bj, pts1)
msgctxt "an4.63:2.1"
msgid "Brahmāti, bhikkhave, mātāpitūnaṃ etaṃ adhivacanaṃ. "
msgstr "‘Brahmā’ is a term for your parents. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.63:2.2"
msgid "Pubbācariyāti, bhikkhave, mātāpitūnaṃ etaṃ adhivacanaṃ. "
msgstr "‘First teachers’ is a term for your parents. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. VAR: Pubbadevatāti → pubbadevāti (bj, s1-3, km)
msgctxt "an4.63:2.3"
msgid "Pubbadevatāti, bhikkhave, mātāpitūnaṃ etaṃ adhivacanaṃ. "
msgstr "‘Old deities’ is a term for your parents. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.63:2.4"
msgid "Āhuneyyāti, bhikkhave, mātāpitūnaṃ etaṃ adhivacanaṃ. "
msgstr "‘Worthy of an offering dedicated to the gods’ is a term for your parents. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.63:2.5"
msgid "Taṃ kissa hetu? "
msgstr "Why is that? "

msgctxt "an4.63:2.6"
msgid "Bahukārā, bhikkhave, mātāpitaro, puttānaṃ āpādakā posakā imassa lokassa dassetāroti. "
msgstr "Parents are very helpful to their children, they raise them, nurture them, and show them the world. "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "an4.63:3.1"
msgid "Brahmāti mātāpitaro, "
msgstr "Parents are said to be ‘Brahmā’ "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an4.63:3.2"
msgid "pubbācariyāti vuccare; "
msgstr "and ‘first teachers’. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an4.63:3.3"
msgid "Āhuneyyā ca puttānaṃ, "
msgstr "They’re worthy of offerings dedicated to the gods from their children, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an4.63:3.4"
msgid "pajāya anukampakā. "
msgstr "for they love their offspring. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc4
msgctxt "an4.63:4.1"
msgid "Tasmā hi ne namasseyya, "
msgstr "Therefore an astute person "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an4.63:4.2"
msgid "sakkareyya ca paṇḍito; "
msgstr "would revere them and honor them "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an4.63:4.3"
msgid "Annena atha pānena, "
msgstr "with food and drink, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an4.63:4.4"
msgid "vatthena sayanena ca; "
msgstr "clothes and bedding, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an4.63:4.5"
msgid "Ucchādanena nhāpanena, "
msgstr "by anointing and bathing, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an4.63:4.6"
msgid "pādānaṃ dhovanena ca. "
msgstr "and by washing their feet. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc5
msgctxt "an4.63:5.1"
msgid "Tāya naṃ pāricariyāya, "
msgstr "Because they look after "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an4.63:5.2"
msgid "mātāpitūsu paṇḍitā; "
msgstr "their parents like this, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an4.63:5.3"
msgid "Idheva naṃ pasaṃsanti, "
msgstr "they’re praised in this life by the astute, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an4.63:5.4"
msgid "pecca sagge pamodatī”ti. "
msgstr "and they depart to rejoice in heaven.” "

#. HTML: </p></blockquote><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an4.63:5.5"
msgid "Tatiyaṃ. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
